'''Crunchyroll'''，簡稱'''CR'''，是美国的一家提供[[东亚|东亚]]相关[[流媒体|流媒体]]影视服务和国际交流社区的网站。

==概要==
于2006年對外宣稱由大學生成立，因架站站長shinji喜歡吃[[壽司|壽司]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/user/shinji |title=Crunchyroll - shinji - Profile Info |accessdate=2013-05-24 |archive-date=2013-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524061210/http://www.crunchyroll.com/user/shinji |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Founder |date= |url=http://wiki.crunchyroll.com/Founder |accessdate= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130070834/http://wiki.crunchyroll.com/Founder |publisher=WIKIROLL! |archivedate=2009-01-30 |language= |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interview/2008-03-25/vu-nguyen Interview: Crunchyroll's Vu Nguyen] {{Wayback|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interview/2008-03-25/vu-nguyen |date=20130601132333 }}. Anime News Network. 2008-03-25.</ref>，遂命名「Crunchyroll」<ref>{{Cite web |title=About |date= |url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/about |accessdate= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060831165655/http://www.crunchyroll.com/about |publisher=Crunchyroll |archivedate=2006-08-31 |language= |deadurl=yes }} 「Crunch roll」是一種美式壽司脆卷。</ref>；實際上這是創辦者當時低調、匿名的手法<ref>[http://techcrunch.com/2007/08/29/crunchyroll-pushes-the-envelope-on-video-copyright/ Crunchyroll Pushes the Envelope On Video Copyright] {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2007/08/29/crunchyroll-pushes-the-envelope-on-video-copyright/ |date=20130528125329 }}. TechCrunch. 2007-08-29.</ref>。Kun Gao為首四人早已2004年從[[柏克萊加州大學|柏克萊加州大學]]畢業<ref>[http://www.ict-summit.jp/2010/en/speakers/index.html#sp6b-4 Mr. Kun Gao] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ict-summit.jp/2010/en/speakers/index.html#sp6b-4 |date=20130516181104 }}. Global ICT Summit 2010.</ref>，白天工作之餘，合夥創立公司、架設網站；後來均自願辭去工作，專心經營<ref>{{Cite web |title=Eta Kappa Nu, Mu Chapter HKN Officers - Fall 2003 |date= |url=http://hkn.eecs.berkeley.edu/about/muchapterofficers-fa03.shtml |accessdate= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080719074022/http://hkn.eecs.berkeley.edu/about/muchapterofficers-fa03.shtml |publisher=UC Berkeley |archivedate=2008-07-19 |language= |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=icv2>{{cite web|url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/13922.html|title=Crunchyroll CEO: Making Online Anime Pay|publisher=ICv2|date=2008-12-15|accessdate=2008-12-15|archive-date=2008-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081217101508/http://www.icv2.com./articles/news/13922.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

起初供[[ACG|ACG]]及[[戲劇|戲劇]]愛好者分享用途，卻也引發侵權爭議。在[[Venrock|Venrock]]公司资助下，走向合法化串流服務逐漸壯大，内容包括[[动画|动画]]、[[漫画|漫画]]、戲劇、[[音乐|音乐]]、[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]和[[赛车|赛车]]等，依授權區域而定。

==沿革==
;2006年
*6月，創建公司及網站。

;2008年
*2月，[[Venrock|Venrock]]投資挹注。{{r|icv2}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://venrock.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=content.contentDetail&id=9404|title=Venrock|publisher=Venrock.com|year=2008|accessdate=2008|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007223822/http://venrock.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=content.contentDetail&id=9404|archivedate=2011-10-07}}</ref>
*9月，日本法人{{nihongo|「Crunchyroll株式會社」|クランチロール株式会社|Crunchyroll Kabushiki Kaisha}}成立，為對日窗口。
*11月，與[[東京電視台|東京電視台]]合作並引進資金。

;2009年
*2月，成為[[日本動畫協會|日本動畫協會]]準會員。

;2010年
*6月，導入[[Bitway|Bitway]]資金。<ref>[http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2010-07-02/crunchyroll-bitway-announce-digital-initiative Crunchyroll and Bitway Announce Digital Manga Initiative] {{Wayback|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2010-07-02/crunchyroll-bitway-announce-digital-initiative |date=20140120024757 }}. Anime News Network. 2010-07-02.</ref>
*8月，取得《[[秒速5公分|秒速5公分]]》代理權，也是首次涉足DVD代理業務<ref>[http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2010-08-13/crunchyroll-adds-shinkai-5-centimeters-per-second-dvd Crunchyroll Adds Shinkai's 5 Centimeters per Second DVD] {{Wayback|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2010-08-13/crunchyroll-adds-shinkai-5-centimeters-per-second-dvd |date=20100815000334 }}. Anime News Network. 2010-08-13.</ref>。

;2012年
*3月，成立英國分站。<ref>[http://www.animenewsnetwork.co.uk/news/2012-03-20/crunchyroll-launches-u.k-page Crunchyroll Launches U.K. Page]{{Dead link|date=2019年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. Anime News Network. 2012-03-20.</ref>
*8月，開通[[PS3|PS3]]、[[PlayStation_Vita|PSV]]服務。
*11月，成立巴西分站。<ref>[http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2012-10-31/crunchyroll-brings-anime-to-brazil Crunchyroll Brings Anime to Brazil] {{Wayback|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2012-10-31/crunchyroll-brings-anime-to-brazil |date=20121204000013 }}. Anime News Network. 2012-10-31.</ref>
*12月，開通[[Xbox_Live|Xbox Live]]服務。

;2013年
*6月，開通[[Apple_TV|Apple TV]]服務<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2013/06/19HBO-GO-WatchESPN-Come-to-Apple-TV.html|title=HBO GO & WatchESPN Come to Apple TV|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]]|date=2013-06-19|accessdate=|archive-date=2013-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629030415/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2013/06/19HBO-GO-WatchESPN-Come-to-Apple-TV.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

*10月，提供「Crunchyroll Manga」線上漫畫服務。

*12月，由闕寧集團（The Chernin Group，TCG）取得[[控制股權|控制股權]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/peter-chernin-takes-control-of-anime-provider-crunchyroll/ |work=Deadline.com |first=David |last=Lieberman |title=Peter Chernin Takes Control Of Anime Provider Crunchyroll |date=2013-12-02 |accessdate=2014-01-14 |archive-date=2013-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204211510/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/peter-chernin-takes-control-of-anime-provider-crunchyroll/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/02/us-chernin-crunchyroll-idUSBRE9B10X320131202 |work=Reuters |first=Ronald |last=Glover |title=Chernin buys anime site Crunchyroll to expand online video assets |date=2013-12-02 |accessdate=2014-01-14 |archive-date=2014-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114002850/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/02/us-chernin-crunchyroll-idUSBRE9B10X320131202 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;2014年
*4月，AT&T和闕寧集團合資成立Otter Media公司來收購、投資及開通[[OTT服務|OTT服務]]，將Crunchyroll納入旗下<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/att-chernin-groups-otter-media-online-video-venture-acquires-creativebug-for-10-mil-1201261983/ |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |first=Todd |last=Spangler |title=AT&T-Chernin Group’s Otter Media Online-Video Venture Acquires Creativebug for $10 Mil |date=2014-07-14 |accessdate=2016-04-12 |archive-date=2016-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422144136/http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/att-chernin-groups-otter-media-online-video-venture-acquires-creativebug-for-10-mil-1201261983/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

;2015年
*8月，報導指出Otter Media開設子公司Ellation整合旗下Crunchyroll、Creativebug和SoompiTV<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2015/digital/news/ellation-otter-media-att-peter-chernin-group-1201555464/ |work=Variety |first=Janko |last=Roettgers |title=Chernin, AT&T Set Brand for New Online Video Venture: Ellation |date=2015-08-03 |accessdate=2016-04-12 |archive-date=2016-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416125304/http://variety.com/2015/digital/news/ellation-otter-media-att-peter-chernin-group-1201555464/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;2016年
*2月，與[[住友商事|住友商事]]共同成立{{nihongo|Crunchyroll SC Anime Fund株式會社|クランチロールSCアニメファンド株式会社}}，從事動畫製作委員会出資、動畫海外營業權取得及販售。
*4月，宣布與[[KADOKAWA|KADOKAWA]]締結戰略同盟，取得其亞洲以外動畫數位發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-press-release/2016/04/10/crunchyroll-and-kadokawa-enter-into-strategic-alliance|title=Crunchyroll and KADOKAWA Enter into Strategic Alliance|publisher=Crunchyroll|date=2016-04-11|accessdate=2016-04-12|archive-date=2016-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413235835/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-press-release/2016/04/10/crunchyroll-and-kadokawa-enter-into-strategic-alliance|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*7月，宣布將推出一系列英文配音的動畫BD/DVD。
*9月，宣布與[[Funimation|Funimation]]合作，兩家交流影音作品提供各自訂戶收看<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-09-08/crunchyroll-funimation-announce-partnership-to-share-content-via-streaming-home-video-est/.106234|title=Crunchyroll, Funimation Announce Partnership to Share Content Via Streaming, Home Video, Est.|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=September 8, 2016|accessdate=2017-04-20|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919222537/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-09-08/crunchyroll-funimation-announce-partnership-to-share-content-via-streaming-home-video-est/.106234|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

;2017年
*2月，宣布付費收視訂戶已破百萬<ref name="Million">{{cite press release|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-press-release/2017/02/09-1/largest-anime-streaming-service-crunchyroll-surpasses-one-million-paid-subscribers|title=Largest Anime Streaming Service Crunchyroll Surpasses One Million Paid Subscribers|publisher=Crunchyroll|date=February 9, 2017|accessdate=February 14, 2017|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215120833/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-press-release/2017/02/09-1/largest-anime-streaming-service-crunchyroll-surpasses-one-million-paid-subscribers|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*3月，開始藉[[Steam|Steam]]平台銷售線上動畫。

;2018年
*1月，Otter Media從[[東京電視臺|東京電視臺]]買下Crunchyroll剩餘20%股份。
*8月，Otter Media與被[[AT&T|AT&T]]收購，連同Crunchyroll納入[[華納媒體|華納媒體]]旗下。
*9月，領導層調整，Kun Gao卸任轉諮詢職務，由Joanne Waage接任總經理。至此當初架站成員皆與公司經營無涉。
*11月，Funimation取消合作，兩家不再交流影音作品提供各自訂戶收看。

;2019年
*3月，Crunchyroll改隸華納媒體娛樂。
*7月，Crunchyroll宣佈與[[Viz_Media|Viz Media]]開始合作。
*9月，入主[[碧日#歐洲|VIZ Media Europe]]，並且成立EMEA（歐洲、中東、非洲）部門，連同統括VIZ Media Europe業務。

;2020年
*1月，VIZ Media Europe SAS公司改名Crunchyroll SAS。
*4月，VIZ Media Europe集團品牌更名Crunchyroll EMEA。
*12月9日，[[索尼影视娱乐|索尼影视娱乐]]預計從美國電話電報公司（AT&T）買下Crunchyroll的全部股份，Crunchyroll成為索尼旗下[[Funimation|Funimation]]的全資子公司。

;2021年
*3月24日，[[美国司法部|美國司法部]]擔心Crunchyroll收購案會減少版權方可選擇的上架平台，故依照[[反壟斷法|反壟斷法]]介入調查<ref>{{Cite web|title=Report: U.S. Justice Department Extends Antitrust Review of Sony's Proposed Acquisition of Crunchyroll|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2021-03-24/report-u.s-justice-department-extends-antitrust-review-of-sony-proposed-acquisition-of-crunchyroll/.171049|access-date=2021-07-26|work=Anime News Network|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713180813/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2021-03-24/report-u.s-justice-department-extends-antitrust-review-of-sony-proposed-acquisition-of-crunchyroll/.171049}}</ref>。

